# Binary fixtures under tests/fixtures/ — keep byte-exact across platforms.
# Git on Windows defaults to core.autocrlf=true, which will LF→CRLF-convert any
# file it sniffs as "text". The PDF fixture in tidyup-extract has hardcoded
# xref byte offsets and breaks at parse time if a single LF gets rewritten to
# CRLF on Windows checkout. Force every binary fixture through as-is.
*.pdf  binary
*.xlsx binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.png  binary
*.mp3  binary
*.wav  binary
*.flac binary
*.ogg  binary
*.onnx binary
